\fs48 VT100 Emulation Preferences\

\fs16 \
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs28 \cf0 The VT100 Emulation view is used to set the VT100 characteristics of Terminal windows.\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs16 \cf0 \
\pard\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \

\fs28 \
	{{\NeXTGraphic F4.tiff \width7840 \height2060 \noorient \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \'93Translate newlines to carriage returns when pasting\'94 should normally be checked.  It\'92s required by some other operating systems, and it works correctly for most UNIX programs.\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs16 \cf0 \
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 If \'93Generate VT100 codes from the keypad\'94 is checked, the keys on the numeric keypad generate VT100 keypad sequences.  Otherwise, the keys on the numeric keypad generate the characters shown on the keys.  Holding down the Alternate key while pressing a key on the numeric keypad toggles the interpretation temporarily.\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs16 \cf0 \
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 If \'93Perform strict VT100 emulation\'94 is checked, some additional (and normally undesirable) aspects of VT100 emulation are strictly enforced:\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs16 \cf0 \
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2480\fi-380\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 \'b7	If you type a Delete character at the left edge of a Terminal window, the command-line cursor won\'92t wrap around to the end of the previous line.  This may make it difficult to edit long command lines that wrap.\

\fs16 \

\fs28 \'b7	Strict DECCOLM handling is enforced.  Otherwise, the DECCOLM escape code to change the window\'92s size is obeyed only if the new size is larger than the old size.\

\fs16 \

\fs28 \'b7	The + key on the numeric keypad generates a comma (,) character.\

\fs16 \
\pard\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \

\fs28 \
	{{\NeXTGraphic F9.tiff \width7840 \height1660 \noorient \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}¬}\
