\fs52 Finding Text in a Terminal Window \

\fs16 \
\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs28 \cf0 The Find panel lets you search for text in the main Terminal window.  To open the Find panel, choose Find Panel in the Find menu.\
\pard\tx2480\tx2860\tx3240\li2100\partightenfactor0

\fs16 \cf0 \
\pard\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \

\fs28 \
