\fs28 \cf0 \'b7	To add a service, click the New button.  A new entry named New Service #1 is added to the service list.  Type the name that you\'92d like to appear in the Services menu, and then configure the service using the controls in the Terminal Services panel.  When you\'92re done, click OK.\

\fs16 \

\fs28 \'b7	To delete a service, select it and click the Remove button.  \

\fs16 \

\fs28 \'b7	To modify a service definition, select its name and then redefine the service using the controls on the Terminal Services panel.  When you\'92re done, click OK.\

\fs16 \
