\f0\b0 \cf0 Font Panel	Displays the standard Font panel, which lets you choose among various fonts, typefaces, and font sizes.  However, only fixed-width fonts, such as Courier and Ohlfs, can be used in Terminal.  Also note that Ohlfs is strictly a screen font \'96 text displayed in Ohlfs prints as Courier instead.\

\fs16 \

\fs28 Bold, Italic	Makes the text in the main Terminal window become bold or italic.\

\fs16 \

\fs28 Larger, Smaller	Makes the text in the main Terminal window become larger or smaller.\

\fs16 \

